{"tid":283180,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"ONE PIECE 869 情報","createTime":"2017-06-14T03:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-18T08:33:39.000Z","uid":19232,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7dbd8e343ac8e992e349d779d9fba3f784d10855","tid":283180,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T03:09:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://onepiece-naruto.com/blog-entry-2730.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fonepiece-naruto.com%2Fblog-entry-2730.html&d=ZtF%2B5Weu0h1QVM77lB%2BB2ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=fff658bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://onepiece-naruto.com/blog-entry-2730.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://imgur.com/a/kfUmx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2Fa%2FkfUmx&d=ZtF%2B5Weu0h1QVM77lB%2BB2ttKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=f1574df5\" target=\"_blank\">http://imgur.com/a/kfUmx</a>"},{"pid":"2f6fbe8a28f922170fc10c4752efb0fea0d6f5e5","tid":283180,"uid":73043,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:30:14.000Z","msg":"無翻譯你post黎把撚呀"},{"pid":"47b8441a9adeef964ecedd3cd0484c3dffa906f2","tid":283180,"uid":19232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"869話 籠城<br />\n根據卡彭的指示進入城堡內躲避的一夥，但是卡塔庫裡把布蕾搶了回來<br />\n娜美和加洛特等人因為big mom的孩子們的攻擊，退避比別人晚了一步<br />\n陷入絕境的時刻穿著戰鬥服的傑爾馬亂入<br />\n彷彿特攝片英雄登場一樣的畫面<br />\n一瞬間擊退了敵人攻擊的傑爾馬，然後也進入卡彭的城堡裡避難<br />\n在混亂中，&ldquo;暗金王&rdquo;路菲爾德試圖打開玉手箱，但是因為big mom的悲鳴，玉手箱直接被吹飛出了蛋糕城<br />\n卡彭想要用城堡的砲台攻擊big mom，但是卡塔庫裡的糯米把砲台封死了無法進行砲擊<br />\n佩羅斯佩羅用糖直接固定住了城堡讓城堡無法行動<br />\n卡彭嘆氣，作戰再次失敗<br />\n卡彭和大家說如果城堡被破壞了，他本人會直接死亡，而且城堡裡面的人也自然會被放出去<br />\n就在說明的時候big mom恢復正常，開始反擊<br />\n城堡的一部分被破壞，沾滿血的卡彭<br />\n完，下週休刊"},{"pid":"19eb2a8f94e320ecf9ef222b353017bc0fdc8b29","tid":283180,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-14T04:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無翻譯你post黎把撚呀</blockquote><br />\n我真係恭喜你呀"},{"pid":"3e65febfded864dd27c9c9c1d684dccd7cd9cff7","tid":283180,"uid":7840,"li